          <lg n="1">
            <l xml:id="swift-261-008D-line-1" n="1">Are the Guests of this house still doom'd to be cheated</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-261-008D-line-2" n="2">Sure the Fates have decreed they by halves should be treated</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-261-008D-line-3" n="3">In the days of good John, if you came here to dine</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-261-008D-line-4" n="4">You had choice of good meat, no choice of good wine</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-261-008D-line-5" n="5">In Jonathan's reign if you come here to eat</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-261-008D-line-6" n="6">You have choice of good wine no choice of good meat</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-261-008D-line-7" n="7">O Jove! then how fully might all sides be blest</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-261-008D-line-8" n="8">Wouldst thou but agree to this humble request</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-261-008D-line-9" n="9">Put both Deans in one, or if that's too much trouble</l>
            <l xml:id="swift-261-008D-line-10" n="10">Instead of the Deans make the Deanery double</l>
          </lg>
        </div>
      </div>
